PrecisEnactment of the TREATY LAND ENTITLEMENT (MANITOBA) REMISSION ORDER which provides for the remission of the tax paid or payable on the supply of land, third party interests and tangible personal property supplied to certain Indian Bands that settle treaty land entitlement claims.
